medium text-slate-700\">Official Party Name<!-- --> <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><input required=\"\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm outline-none transition focus:border-[#0B1F3A] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#0B1F3A]/10\" placeholder=\"e.g. Alliance for Student Progress\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Party Acronym<!-- --> <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><input required=\"\" maxLength=\"10\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm outline-none transition focus:border-[#0B1F3A] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#0B1F3A]/10\" placeholder=\"e.g. ASP\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><label class=\"mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Party Motto<!-- --> </label><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm outline-none transition focus:border-[#0B1F3A] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#0B1F3A]/10\" placeholder=\"e.g. Unity, Progress, Excellence\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><label class=\"mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Party Description<!-- --> </label><textarea rows=\"3\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm outline-none transition focus:border-[#0B1F3A] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#0B1F3A]/10\" placeholder=\"Brief description of the party&#x27;s vision and objectives...\"></textarea></div></div></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"mb-6 border-b border-slate-100 pb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Party Leadership</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500\">Names of the party&#x27;s registered executive leadership.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\"><div><label class=\"mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700\">Chairperson Full Name<!-- --> <span class=\"text-red-500\">*</span></label><i